🟡 方案 2（更安全）：先丟 temp table

如果你想「像 1 / 2 標籤但不污染原表」：

SELECT *,
       ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY
                TemplateId,
                GroupId,
                Parameter1,
                Parameter2,
                Parameter3,
                Parameter4,
                Parameter5,
                Parameter6,
                Parameter7,
                Parameter8,
                Parameter9,
                Parameter10,
                Score,
                Enabled,
                Deleted,
                Repeatable,
                Category,
                qryId
            ORDER BY ID
       ) AS RN
INTO #tmp
FROM BSADBTW..HRS_QuerySyntaxes;

然後：

DELETE A
FROM BSADBTW..HRS_QuerySyntaxes A
JOIN #tmp T ON A.ID = T.ID
WHERE T.RN > 1;

